National wastewater surveillance of SARS-CoV-2 in Denmark

General information

In this document, you will find the results for the national wastewater surveillance of SARS-CoV-2 that can be generated based on the data that can be downloaded from Data from the National Wastewater Surveillance of SARS-CoV-2 week xx xxx (.zip)

For further information and a description of the data, please refer to readme-spildevand.pdf, which is also available for download alongside the data.

Results until week 24

The figures below show the weekly aggregated numbers for the concentrations of SARS-CoV-2 concentrations in the wastewater. The results are available on national and regional levels. The variable rna_mean_faeces has been used as input.
